description:
Kyle Baker brings his manic energy to this collection of PLASTIC MAN #1-6, featuring a new "plastic" cover! Plas, with sidekick Woozy Winks, gets into all sorts of trouble as his not-so-innocent past as criminal "Eel" O'Brian comes back to haunt him!

[Note: listed as softcover, cover is a pliable plastic cover.]
name: Plastic Man: On The Lam

description:
Trapped by Temptation (5 pages)

Flatter Your Type (1 page)

Homecoming (1 page)

My Dark Past (5 pages)

Campaign for Love (5 pages)

Your Problem (1 page)

Betrayed by Love (1 page)

Price-Tag on Passion (5 pages)
name: Trapped by Temptation

description: MARVEL DIGITAL COMICS EXCLUSIVE Before she became RESCUE, Pepper Potts was still a force to be reckoned with! In this untold tale, Tony Stark's right hand woman's morning routine takes a dangerous detour when she finds herself caught in an elaborate subway heist! Without Iron Man to call on, Pepper's going to have to put a cap on this caper on her own!
name: Killer Commute

description: The New Green Hornet and Kato renew their fathers' war on crime, but even as they clean up the streets of Century City, the Black Hornet musters his forces for a final confrontation with the gang-busting duo. Britt Reid assumes his father's role as publisher of The Sentinel and quickly uncovers a plot to unleash a hellish new war machine that will imperil not only his city, but the world. Fighting a war on two fronts, the young Green Hornet reaches his breaking point.
name: Episode Seven: The Son Also Rises

description: It's Batman and Superman vs. the undead! The Dark Knight and The Man of Steel join forces with a vampire and a werewolf to stop the nefarious Professor Combs from unleashing a vile Voodoo spell upon the world. But will even the combined might of the World's Finest be enough to stop the powers of Hell? Be here to find out!
name: Batman vs The Undead Part Five: The Waking Dead

description: They say the greatest trick the Devil ever pulled was convincing the world he didn’t exist…Wait. That wasn’t “they.” It was Kevin Spacey, in The Usual Suspects. Anyway, Wade Wilson -- a.k.a. Deadpool -- seems to have the opposite problem. He’s having a damned hard time convincing the world that he does exist, that he’s been a brave soldier on the front lines of America’s secret wars for more than two decades. Now his former partner Domino is pointing a gun at Wilson’s head on live TV, telling a panel of Senators that he’s full of [REDACTED]. But when the truth finally does emerge, the walls will come tumbling down and everybody will be caught in the crossfire just the way Deadpool likes it. Don’t miss the conclusion of Duane (Cable) Swierczynski’s and artist Jason (Body Bags) Pearson’s full-tilt double-barrel assault on reality
name: This Time, It's Personal

description: In this Issue the mighty War Dancer explores this reality and contemplates it's destruction, He is attacked at a private home by Soldiers from the Org of Plasm, He defeats them then kills a Little Girl!!!! Crazy stuff.
name: From Eternity To Here

description: War Dancer journeys to the Org of Plasm to fight Centurion Massac and gets his arm ripped off!
name: Alone and Unarmed

description: War Dancer pursues Centurion Massac to The Wrestling rings of the CWA on Earth to finish their battle..
name: Tag Team Terror

description: War Dancer and Charlemagne face off again and take the fight all the way to the Org of Plasm.
name: The Dancer Dreams

description: War Dancer grants his friend Billy Ballistic the ability to fly and see into the sub-stratum then they get in a bar fight..
name: Lead Him Not Into Temptation

description: War Dancer and Charlemagne meet in Angor Wat for their Final Battle. Final Issue.
name: To be or not..In Angkor Wat!

description:
SO MANY HULKS, ONE BOOK A MONTH WASN”T ENOUGH TO HOLD THEM! Bruce Banner is the Hulk once again, and far from being left alone, he’s got a whole family of gamma-charged allies at his side. Son Skaar, daughter Lyra, cousin She-Hulk, friends A-Bomb and Korg, and wife Red She-Hulk—or is that EX-wife? Meanwhile, a universe away, Hiro-Kala, the mysterious DARK SON of Hulk, rises to power on the planer K’ai. He has a plan for his long lost family members, and it involves a bigger smash than his father has ever made. The Incredible Greg Pak (PLANET HULK) kicks off the DARK SON story as INCREDIBLE HULKS begins a new TWICE MONTHLY schedule!
 

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter One: Earth
  • Chapter Two: K'Ai
name: Dark Son, Part One

description: One-Shot
name: Fire From Heaven!

description: The ARTIFACTS lead-in series reaches its penultimate issue! Just as Dani and Finch's relationship reaches a turning point, Dani must embrace the role of the Angelus once again, finally facing down an enemy who has lurked in the shadows and plotted her doom. Forced to make a choice between her humanity and her life as the Angelus, what will Dani choose?
name: Illumination, Part 5

description: Welcome to the Biological World of Plasm, Where the weak are mulched for the greater good of the Org! Lorca learns about the value of uniqueness in this issue.
name: "The Death of Love" Sedition Agenda Prologue

description:
Manga Contents

  • Shurayuki-hime

Young Britt Reid has just lost his father at the hands of the mysterious Black Hornet. As blinding rage threatens to overwhelm him he encounters a long lost enemy of the original Green Hornet: A man who may hold the key to Britt's salvation, or his destruction. This Green Hornet Annual reveals an untold tale from Kevin Smith's Green Hornet series and sets the stage for future Green Hornet sagas.
name: The Straight and Narrow

description: In this three issue mini-series,the writer shows us how did Auberon became the king Faerie.
name: TPB

description: As the Young Allies are well aware, when the Bastards of Evil strike, they strike hard! Separated, scrambling, and with lives on the line, can the Young Allies pull together fast enough to survive?
name: Now, Not Tomorrow Part 4: The Lie

description: The origins of your favorite X-Men written and drawn by the best in the industry collected in one place! Cyclops! Wolverine! Magneto! All the big characters origins boiled down to one beautiful page that every reader will cut out and tape up on their wall!
name: Origins Of Marvel Comics: X-Men

description: Teamed with the dirge of Shotgun City's police force, Johnny Jackson is thrust into confrontation against Hunt Cassidy and his band of, their sinister influence having put the city on edge. And when Hunt realizes that a precious possession is missing, the full extent of the madness is revealed...
name: Beast Cops

description: Exploring “pop-culture as religion”, this issue we discover the mysterious stalker in the shadow world of cinematic icons; THE PROJECTIONIST!
name: Celluloid From The Void

description: The June Alley Inn, located in the western mouse city of Barkstone, is lively as a throng of mice excitedly spin fantastic yarns in a storytelling contest! One such tall tale is about a pauper mouse who risks life and limb to find the best gift for the most-eligible young lady mouse in town.
name: A Mouse Named Fox; The Critic; The Ballad of Nettledown; The Raven

volume.name: Mouse Guard: Legends of the Guard

description: The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles are back and better than ever! The Purple Dragons, a violent street gang stalking New York's streets, need to be taught a lesson and Splinter's students are on the case. Little do they know that an ancient enemy lurks at the heart of this gangland violence.
name: Things Change

description: More teenage Image heroes guest star as the fight against the alien menace continues. Meanwhile, Wraith gets a shocking look at his heritage. Plus, in our exclusive back-up series, NOTORIOUS is targeted by the assassin Omerta!
name: Sins of the Father, Part 3 of 5

description: A stunning Prestige one-shot casts Captain Janeway and her crew as figures in a real-life fairy tale as the Doctor goes on an urgent mission alone on a strange planet's surface.
name: Avalon Rising

description: Casey Jones has some serious anger issues to work out and the only way he can do that is by bashing Purple Dragon heads. You know Casey's anger issues are serious if Raphael is the voice of reason during a fight. But when the masked maniac decides to throw down with the meanest turtle in the bunch, Raphael sees red and the rest you'll have to see for yourself.
name: Meet Casey Jones

description: Baxter Stockman recollects the events that transformed him into an evil genius just before the turtles track him to his underground lab.  Now it's mousers vs. turtles in a battle royale you need to see to believe!
name: Attack of the Mousers

description: In the sewers deep beneath New York's bustling sidewalks April O'Neil finds herself face-to-face with Baxter Stockman's malevolent mechanical mousers.  The young computer programmer needs help of the kind only a quartet of Ninja Turtles can provide!
name: A Better Mousetrap

description:
When a group of religious extremists called the Redeemers target the planet Haresh for "purification", Captain Calhoun of the Starship USS Excalibur is outraged. He orders the ship to Haresh to intervene... but on the way there, an emergency rescue on another planet slows the Excalibur down, so that it arrives too late. Haresh is already a dead planet. 
 
Calhoun doesn't take defeat lightly, though... so he tries a risky scheme to travel back in time, arriving at Haresh early enough to save the populace from the Redeemers. This maneuver isn't universally popular, though, either with his crew or the Federation timeship USS Relativity. That ship's Captain Braxton is prepared to use force against the Starship USS Excalibur, in the pursuit of his mission to keep the timeline intact. 
 
With the Federation on one side and the Redeemers on the other, Calhoun is a man in the crossfire. And there's no easy way out..
name: Double Time

volume.name: Star Trek: New Frontier - Double Time

description: Sins of Youth part 4 of 12. Heavy is the head that wears the crown of the King...unless he gets de-aged, forgets all his responsibilities, and parties on with the monstrous Lagoon Man! But the currents of change aren't restricted to Aquaboy alone, his old (now young) foe Black Manta is out to regain his humanity, even if it means corrupting all undersea life!
name: Turning Back The Tides of Time
Uncanny X-Men: The Coming of Bishop

volume.name: Uncanny X-Men: The Coming of Bishop

description: Collects Uncanny X-Men #320, #321 and X-Men #40, #41.
name: X-Men: Legionquest

description: With the world at war, Bucky Barnes and the original Young Allies find themselves amid the surreal settings of a Hollywood back lot, under attack from the mind-bending power of Lady Lotus. Decades later, Bucky has become Captain America -- and now must return to the site of the Allies' greatest defeat, to stop Lotus before she can reclaim the power to control all humankind! Roger Stern (CAPTAIN AMERICA #600), Nick Dragotta (THE MANY LOVES OF THE AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) and Marco Santucci (X-FACTOR) unite to tell an era-spanning epic that they call "Havoc in Hollywood!"
name: Havok in Hollywood

description: Collects: Age of Apocalypse: The Chosen (1995) #1, Cable (1993) #20, X-Men Alpha (1995) #1
name: X-Men: Dawn of the Age of Apocalypse

volume.name: X-Men: Dawn of the Age of Apocalypse

description: After escaping from the Malmori warship, Zed and Nell must now cross the deadly Lambda Zone, avoiding the pirates known as The Jackers who reside there. Meanwhile at Oztem, preparations begin for the final battle for possession of the Oztems' replication technology. Some will live. And some will die.

volume.name: Roger Corman Presents: Battle Amongst the Stars

description:
Witness the birth of the most important super hero team ever in a universe-spanning event that will rock the month of March! Wade Wilson has been tapped to save the Universe, and to do that he's going to need help. Enter: The sexy-but-insecure Lady Deadpool! The devious-but-lovable Headpool (a.k.a. the Zombie Deadpool Head)! The bratty-but-brilliant Kidpool! And the irascible mutt known as Dogpool! Individually, they're well, kind of messed up, but together, they're the unstoppable force known as DPC. 
 
 Collects Prelude to Deadpool Corps #1-5.
name: Prelude to Deadpool Corps

description:
Little X-Men! Big Adventure! Stars Reborn! Things have changed in Mojoworld as Mojo's been ousted by Mr. Veech, who's replaced the The X-Babies - the number one, top-rated stars - with something newer, safer, friendlier, and...more adorable! The X-Babies we know and love aren't going to sit by and let that happen. And how are the characters from Marvel's mid-'80s, kid-centric Star Comics line involved?

 

 Collects X-Babies #1-4.
name: X-Babies: Stars Reborn
Where It All Began; Keep It In The Family; Less Is More; What You See; You Get What You Pay For

description: A GRIM HUNT TIE-IN! Full of intrigue, action, and adventure, the solo adventure of The Black Cat comes to a dramatic turning point. With Spider-Man facing problems of his own, it's up to Felicia Hardy to face down the family who have been coming after both her and everyone's favorite wall-crawler!
name: The Trophy Hunters, Part 3

description:
In the unending quest to procure the precious Teardrops of the Moon, Mahiru moves in with the Lunar Race. While plans for stealing the next Drop begin to emerge, Mahiru's conscience gives her reservations about joining the bandits, leading to the death of a comrade...and the appearance of a mysterious vortex that takes no prisoners! 

Chapter Titles 

  • Waiting For the Moon - The Descendant of the Princess Meets the Demons Part 3 
  • Waiting For the Moon - The Descendant of the Princess Meets the Demons Part 4 
  • Waiting For the Moon - The Descendant of the Princess Meets the Demons Part 5 
  • The Chapter of the First Moon - The Demons Encounter and Battle An Ancient Enemy Part 1
name: Vol. 2

description:
The battle between humans and the Lunar Race escalates! Mahiru supports the Lunar Race, while her psychic classmate Keiko backs Dawn's Venus--a group of humans whose goal is to annihilate the Lunar Race. As the conflict draws everyone closer into the shadow of the valley of death, Mahiru realizes that the only way to end the bloody conflict is to give peace a chance. 

Chapter Titles 

  • The Chapter of the First Moon - The Demons Battle An Ancient Enemy Part 2 
  • The Chapter of the First Moon - The Demons Battle An Ancient Enemy Part 3 
  • The Chapter of the First Moon - The Demons Battle An Ancient Enemy Part 4 
  • The Chapter of the Crescent Moon - An Ancient Capital Where Thoughts Are Stirred and Shaken Part 1 
  • The Chapter of the Crescent Moon - An Ancient Capital Where Thoughts Are Stirred and Shaken Part 2
name: Vol. 3

description:
When Keiko learns of a possible connection between Mahiru and the Moon Light Bandits, she confronts Mahiru, going as far as branding her as an enemy and traitor. However, the ever-gregarious Mahiru extends a friendly invitation to Keiko in order to calm an increasingly tense situation. Will she take hold of the olive branch? Or will the alliance snap like a twig? 

Chapter Titles 

  • The Chapter of the Crescent Moon - The Demons Encounter and Battle An Ancient Enemy Part 3 
  • The Chapter of the Misty Moon - When Dark Gouds Obscure the Light of the Moon and Stars Part 1 
  • The Chapter of the Misty Moon - When Dark Gouds Obscure the Light of the Moon and Stars Part 2 
  • The Chapter of the Misty Moon - When Dark Gouds Obscure the Light of the Moon and Stars Part 3
name: Vol. 4

description:
The bloody battle between the Moonlight Bandits and Dawn's Venus wages on, and the results are deadly! Volatile love may be lost in the fray and one relationship comes to an end while another one begins to blossom. When Mahiru is taken to the Moon Palace, will she be able to overcome her own pain and suffering in order to save the Empress? 

Chapter Titles 

  • The Chapter of the Misty Moon - When Dark Gouds Obscure the Light of the Moon and Stars Part 4 
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 1 
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 2 
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 3 
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 4
name: Vol. 5

description:
In a desperate move, Nozomu and the Moonlight Bandits send Hokuto and Mutsura a ransom note, telling them to bring the stolen Teardrop of the Moon to a prearranged location, or Hokuto's fiance will be killed. Meanwhile, Mahiru is guided by a friendly spirit to Lake Biwa, the resting place of the seventh and final Teardrop of the Moon...but it is a place where danger awaits as well. Now Mahiru and her companions must find a way to break the magical seal protecting the Teardrop...before it's too late!

Chapter Titles

  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 5
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 6
  • The Chapter of the Moon Palace - The Descendant of the Moon Seeks the Light As the Capital Sinks Into Darkness Part 7
  • The Chapter of the Shining Moon - A Mysterious Lake Where the Moon, Stars and Sun Meet Part 1
  • The Chapter of the Shining Moon - A Mysterious Lake Where the Moon, Stars and Sun Meet Part 2
name: Vol. 6

description: Nagi has been noticing the stare of a particular student at his part-time modeling job at an art school. Kaji seems friendly enough, but Nagi is afraid to let him know his biggest secret--Nagi is a fledgling drag queen and is saving up for some big changes! Will Kaji accept Nagi for who he is or will Nagi be snubbed once again? ...From the creator of You Will Fall in Love and Liberty Liberty comes this cute and romantic story where acceptance can mean being yourself.
name: Vol. 1
Los Misterios de la Muralla China - 25o. Capítulo

description: Sumiko Amakawa's Cross spins a gothic tale about a young, tortured priest with a holy gift that is a blessing--and a curse! All hell breaks loose when our saintly hero excises demons, pushing him to the brink of insanity. Will a fated meeting with a mysterious girl make his path easier to navigate...or lead him to the heart of darkness?
name: Vol. 1

description: A Doppelganger is after Takara's eyes and will find any way to get them. But Takara's power is no match for the Doppelganger. What is the extent of the powers that lie within Takara?
name: Vol. 2

description: Shizuha is unable to sleep since returning from the Vatican. She receives some incense from a nun at Holy Cross Academy and discovers that there is something very special about it indeed. The strange happenings lead her to the suffering nun, but also take her down a nightmarish path brought on by the intriguing incense and Takara must dispel the mystery of the incense in order to save her.
name: Vol. 3

description: The mystery of Sister Caterina continues. When Takara discovers the abhorrent secret of her past and the truth behind her current "pregnancy" he decides to perform an exorcism. Meanwhile, Shizuha's empathic abilities come to the fore, as she too suffers Caterina's pain. And when a confrontation with a student reveals yet another case of possession, Takara imbues Shizuha with the power of the Cross so that she may aide him in the exorcism. All the while it becomes increasingly difficult for these two to contain their feelings for one another.
name: Vol. 4

description: The plot thickens as Takara and Shizuha must unravel the mystery of a young girl with bleeding hands. A terrifying blast detonates in a hotel, killing hundreds of people, and triggers within Shizuha the appearance of the Scriptura. After taking Shizuha to a safe location, Takara sees the Archangel Gabriel appear within her. Further details of Takara's past and his abilities are revealed as new friends and enemies alike are introduced. Shizuka is attacked and Takara must defend her in this exciting volume of Cross!
name: Vol. 5

description:
A dream internship turns into tragic nightmare when five bright, aspiring investigators are handed their first case--the gruesome murder of a peer...  When 15-year-old Kiyomi Hudson signs up for an internship with the Las Vegas Crime Lab, she knows what she's getting into, but she never imagines how deep it will go. She and four fellow interns are allowed to observe the investigation into the murder of Gretchen Yates, but as they start their own research into the events leading to Gretchen's untimely demise, they discover the truth behind an unthinkable crime! Based on the groundbreaking television franchise, here is the story of CSI's future: the CSI interns! 

Chapter Titles  

  • Prologue
  • Chapter One: The Devil's in the Details
  • Chapter Two: Killer Instinct
  • Chapter Three: The Killer Among Us
  • Chapter Four: Prints of the City
  • Chapter Five: Finger of Blame
name: Vol. 1

volume.name: CSI: Crime Scene Investigation - Intern at Your Own Risk
